Dialogue: 3,0:21:38.11,0:21:39.90,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}喂喂　先等等
Dialogue: 3,0:21:40.11,0:21:42.28,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}太刺激的內容
Dialogue: 3,0:21:42.70,0:21:46.41,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}放到最後再說吧
Dialogue: 3,0:21:46.62,0:21:50.70,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}現實中滿是不如意
Dialogue: 3,0:21:51.04,0:21:55.33,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}那就都塞到瓶子裡
Dialogue: 3,0:21:55.92,0:21:58.46,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}準備好參加派對了嗎?
Dialogue: 3,0:21:58.46,0:22:00.46,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}不等你了哦
Dialogue: 3,0:22:01.01,0:22:04.51,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}另一個故事就要開始了
Dialogue: 3,0:22:05.22,0:22:07.39,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}無數氣泡呼呼冒出
Dialogue: 3,0:22:07.51,0:22:09.64,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}無數氣泡啵啵破裂
Dialogue: 3,0:22:09.89,0:22:13.23,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}生活就像汽水
Dialogue: 3,0:22:13.98,0:22:16.40,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}無論是爸爸媽媽的事
Dialogue: 3,0:22:16.52,0:22:18.69,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}還是悶在心底的回憶
Dialogue: 3,0:22:18.77,0:22:23.11,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}都會化作氣泡消失掉
Dialogue: 3,0:22:23.61,0:22:25.70,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}哭泣憂愁又煩惱
Dialogue: 3,0:22:25.91,0:22:27.91,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}無數往事多紛擾
Dialogue: 3,0:22:28.20,0:22:31.62,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}都沒關係的
Dialogue: 3,0:22:32.29,0:22:34.79,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}所有往事盡懷抱
Dialogue: 3,0:22:34.79,0:22:37.04,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}塞進瓶子使勁搖
Dialogue: 3,0:22:37.04,0:22:41.34,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}噗嗤全部釋放　大家一起歡笑
Dialogue: 3,0:22:41.42,0:22:44.59,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}咕嚕嚕　瞬間滿是氣泡
